## Run benchmarks

Progress logs stream below as each lane warms up and runs. This cell can take a long time
(multiple model loads + generation runs per checkpoint/lane) — run it, then move on to the
results cells below once it finishes.

```elixir
results =
  checkpoints
  |> Enum.reject(& &1.skip?)
  |> Enum.shuffle()
  |> Enum.map(fn checkpoint ->
    try do
      {:ok, Runner.run_checkpoint(checkpoint, cfg)}
    rescue
      exception -> {:error, checkpoint.label, Exception.format(:error, exception, __STACKTRACE__)}
    end
  end)

:ok
```

